<package version="1.0">
  <name>Gtk_ScrollingLabel</name>
  <summary>A scrolling label for PHP-Gtk</summary>
  <description>  This is a class to encapsulate the functionality needed for a scrolling gtk label. This class provides a simple, easy to understand API for setting up and controlling the label.  It allows for the ability to scroll in either direction, start and stop the scroll, pause and unpause the scroll, get and set the text, and set display properites of the text.</description>
